<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>bḥbk mnk ạrwny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 (bḥbk mnk ạ̉rwyny yạ ḥby wyạ ạḥly̱ snyny lạ̉nk ạ̉nt ạlḥyạẗ bnwr ạlḥq bthdyny)2
 mryḍ bḥbk bsẖtạq ạ̉mrḍ ạktr bạlạ̉sẖwạq
 mskyn ạlly ḥbk mạ dạq nfsh btbqy̱ mskynh (ʿ ạ̹smk ạ̉nạ tsmyt llạ̉bd rḥ tḥyyny wbạlgẖrbẗ yạmạ ḥnyt ʿạlsḥạb tlạqyny)2
 (ʿlmny ḥbk ạ̉ktr mn qlby wmn kyạny
 wʿ zyt srạjy ạ̹shr ạ̉ntẓrk trjʿ tạny)2
 (lgẖyrk rby tskr mhmạ bqwẗ ạ̉gẖrạny
 bwjwdk ʿmry zhr wbqrbk ṣạr mkạny)2</lyrics>
<author>jmylẗ ṭnws, sbrjn whbẗ</author>
<hymn_number>7249</hymn_number>
</song>